Installation

optional (but recommended) dependencies:
- guess_language: http://code.google.com/p/guess-language/
- PyMe: http://pyme.sourceforge.net/

for python >= 2.6

  python setup.py install --user
  export PATH=$PATH:~/.local/bin

for python 2.5:

  python setup.py install --prefix ~/.local
  export PYTHONPATH=~/.local/lib/python2.5/site-packages
  export PATH=$PATH:~/.local/bin


For removal, just delete all installed files:

  rm -rvf ~/.local/bin/muttlearn ~/.local/lib/python*/site-packages/muttlearn*
